title: The Invitation - Thriller 2016 Eng Fre Ita Multi-Subs 1080p
description:
The Invitation.
In Los Angeles, Will is driving to a dinner party with his girlfriend Kira 
invited by his ex-wife Eden and her new husband David. Will and Eden were in 
love with each other but when their beloved son Ty died, Eden vanished. Now 
she has returned apparently healed with David from Mexico where they 
participated in a mysterious cult. Eden invites her old friends Gina, who is 
waiting for her always late boyfriend Choi; the gays Tommy and Miguel; the 
couple Ben and Claire for the dinner party. David also invites to the party 
the promiscuous Sadie and the weird Pruitt that they have met in the cult. 
Soon Will notes that the house now have security bars in the windows and 
David has closed all the exit doors. Further, David is trying to brainwash 
the guests with messages from his cult. He also finds a strong pill in the 
bedside table and he suspects David and Eden want to poison the guests. When 
he finds a message from Choi in his cellular, Will also believes they have 
killed Gina's boyfriend. Is Will paranoid or having a premonition?
